[genericglass Highball] Serving Glass: Highball With Ice

In Mixing Glass With Ice Add:
2 oz [genericingredient Gin] Beefeater Gin
1/4 oz [genericingredient Triple Sec] Hiram Walker Triple Sec
1 tsp Powder Sugar
1 oz [genericingredient Lemon Juice] Lemon Juice
2 oz [genericingredient Orange Juice] Orange Juice
Shake and Strain
Top: Club Soda
Garnish: Orange Slice

